programme.title: Joel Osteen S3
programme.desc: Hear the messages of hope that best-selling author, evangelist and the senior pastor of Lakewood Church in Houston, Joel Osteen is delivering in each episode. Joel's positive and encouraging speeches will allow viewers to hear God's message of hope, love and victory and be inspired to do great things in life. Joel tries to teach Biblical principles in a simple way, always highlighting the power and importance of love and positive thinking.

programme.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (Rock Star's Miami Mansion & Billionaire's Custom Train) S1 (n°605)
programme.desc: «Rock Star's Miami Mansion & Billionaire's Custom Train»Rock out in the Miami Mansion where Lenny Kravitz left some posh personal touches. Enter "The Vault," an uber-exclusive car club for a group of billionaire neighbors. Be dazzled by the one-of-a-kind pieces of jewelry hiding secret treasures where you'd least expect. Hop on board the train that cost business tycoon John Paul DeJoria millions to customize. Hitch a $6,000 ride on a private seaplane for a luxe weekend in the Hamptons. Run up your bar tab with a nearly $40,000 bottle of cognac. Tour the one-of-a-kind townhouse just steps away from Madonna's Upper East Side mansion. Check out the $20 million sports memorabilia collection that includes a massive sneaker stockpile. And go under the hood of the vintage hot rods that are being transformed into million-dollar modern marvels.
